
Configure to run as virtual host in apache (on MacOSX):

1. add www.proglog.org to /etc/hosts

2. create /Library/WebServer/Documents/proglog directory

3. build application, copy <proglog>/app to dir, created in #2

4. copy proglog.conf to /etc/apache2/other

5 fix access rights on /Library/WebServer/Documents/proglog

6. restart apache:
sudo apachectl restart

